        <header id="ind">Industry 4.0</header>
        <p id="intro">
            Industry 4.0 is a name given to the current trent of automation and data
            exchange in manufacturing technologies. It includes cyber-physical systems, the Internet
            of things, cloud computing and cognitive computing. Industry 4.0 is commonly reffered
            to as the fourth industrial revolution.<br />Wikipedia
        </p>
    </section>
